title: You Need To Calm Down
description:
Taylor Swift was shocked when her friend asked her a simple question.. If he didn't know her stance, then the public definitely didn't.. so she wrote a catchy song with powerful lyrics as her statement! Plus this really pretty music video is filled with Easter eggs!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There's lots of ways to reach us!
